idea:
Meetings and OfficesMeetingsandoffices.com is the co-share space for co-working spaces. A complete end to end solution with search, compare, credibility verification (verifications are carried out while listing, but more importantly user ratings are built in), book online and pay. After just a few minutes on the web application the user can simply reach the venue and get straight to work.&nbsp;

The tagline ‘workspaces your style’ was adopted with lot of aforethought. The workspace paradigm is extraordinarily diverse and that is a huge promise to make to people with so many different tastes and appetites. Meetingsandoffices.com has been built to ensure it is delivered with every interaction.

Meetingsandoffices.com curates verified &amp; quality meeting &amp; conference facilities, day offices, shareable workspaces, and office spaces for lease.
